  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> What's the difference? What is removed from React in Preact that we don't use?\r\n\r\nThere's a good explanation: https://preactjs.com/guide/differences-to-react\r\n\r\nThruth is that we chose React without worrying about the filesize first but it does WEIGH a lot (not 80kb gzipped still).\r\n\r\nWe had multiple users reporting filesize as an issue.\r\n\r\nWhen we target \"vanilla JS\" developers then inlining REACT inside our library can be seen like inlining prototype.js inside a jQuery plugin.\r\n",
    "created_at": "2016-05-25T13:53:09Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1030#issuecomment-221582901",
