  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm all for trimming down the huge filesize. If going to Preact reduces the filesize that much, we definitely need to try a POC. In the end I'd like to have an instantsearch.js v2 that is not so tightly tied to React, but in the short term if we can address the main issue of the filesize with such a quick win, I'm all for it :)\n",
